{"tid":1420701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會唔會今次大家真係中左計 冇人講既???","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:11:57.000Z","uid":267471,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8348551408f68a79aaff6b217fee15fe8777047b","tid":1420701,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得對上721 元朗單野 班人既目的係咩<br />\n係想轉移<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 上環係天橋開槍 全晚既濫暴行為</span></span><br />\n而且<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上環清場行動係同 元朗黑社會出黎打人 係 同 一 時 間</span></span><br />\n目的係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">轉移視線</span></span>!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢班收錢黑社會出黎既目的就係幫政府轉移視線 將大家焦點放去第二到<br />\n咁所以尋日就應該係政權有一單野<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">需要極急地轉移視線 唔想比我地煲大黎做<br />\n</span></span>所以先出左成班老黑 仲要得幾十個 好懷疑係成班臨危受命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為應該有一單野 真係急到要即刻揾人出黎轉移視線<br />\n我視前想後 諗黎諗去 我覺得尋晚政權最擔心 而且事件都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同一時間</span></span>既<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 黃大仙熄燈清場</span></span><br />\n因為熄燈清場本身已經係極陰濕 唔想比記者影到佢地既暴力手段 <br />\n而且 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熄燈清場係會勾起大家對64既 本能性恐懼</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無論 香港定外國所有媒體<br />\n都一定對熄燈清場係有極大恐懼<br />\n好驚我地煲大黎講 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">引起國際間全面反感同企係我地呢邊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以為左唔好中佢計 希望文宣組可以做野 全力煲大件事黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為呢單野 係一定可以引起國際間既關注 至少多對眼睇住 班狗唔多唔少都有少少唔敢濫暴<br />\n大家睇下下方條片 就知其實成件事係幾咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tiffanyoyo/videos/10162025843595371/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftiffanyoyo%2Fvideos%2F10162025843595371%2F&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=e7e7eef8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tiffanyoyo/videos/10162025843595371/</a>"},{"pid":"29070868875c9c9ce6d89bbdc2fcebbbe8029c4c","tid":1420701,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:32:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩開錯台 而家時事台再開返個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9281268f12458cdea3705a0a323b41e33145a0","tid":1420701,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87604f15c75f4b872bee793c6567899336281f2a","tid":1420701,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:33:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0df00d3995242db5d6ab0954d14c7b55b1e044","tid":1420701,"uid":44115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9c251909fd46beec0a314dc6bc6aa90d5ab7bc8","tid":1420701,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a258c28453b58207aa84af6c5b99acd780df239c","tid":1420701,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0a2366e3eb3ae6e3fc13979247b2643df99a21","tid":1420701,"uid":209865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:34:06.000Z","msg":"真係認真唔係派膠既話建議重開op標題唔好有中計二字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150be311f4911a187313a4d9b6d3374eaedb1133",